ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectProtocol to the North Atlantic Treaty on the Accession of the Republic of the Kingdom of Sweden
PrecisOrder authorizing (1) the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, on behalf of Canada, subject to ratification, a protocol to the North Atlantic Treaty on the Accession of the Republic of Finland; and (2) the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to ratify, on behalf of Canada, the PROTOCOL TO THE NORTH ATLANTIC TREATY ON THE ACCESSION OF THE KINGDOM OF SWEDEN.
